{%- comment -%}
  Price Alerts Email (FULL HTML)
  - Locale normalization + RTL detection
  - COUNTRY-BASED locale resolution for ambiguous languages (pt/pt-br, es/es-419, en/en-gb, fr/fr-ca)
  - HERO image per locale
  - Footer localization (prefs + terms)
  - UPDATED: i18n map values replaced with your sheet translations (subject/preheader/headline/body1/body2/cta)
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign lang = customer.language | default: "en" | downcase | replace: "_", "-" -%}
{%- assign lang2 = lang | slice: 0, 2 -%}
{%- assign locale_key = lang2 -%}

{%- comment -%} Country code for resolving ambiguous locales (pt vs pt-br, es vs es-419, etc.)
